history.content: According to @6559, it might no longer be available for this semester (although that post was about 194-26, the advisor response is in general for special topics courses). I saw on CalCentral about 2 weeks ago that CS194-138 was listed, but when I checked back today. There was only one class listed for special topics (CS194-26).

Would anyone know if the class was cancelled? If not, may I have the CCN since it is not on Schedule Planner anymore?

Thanks!
